 that you can rest in the knowledge that buying our product means that you hold the earth in the highest regard.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Who is Aya</h3>\r\n<p>Aya is a west African Goddess of forests, she protects the forest and its animals and she teaches her tribe how to use the plants to sustain and heal themselves.  We chose the name Aya because we align with her values.</p>','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','287-revision-v1','','','2018-08-31 10:50:50','2018-08-31 10:50:50','',287,'http://blog.calloftheforest.com/287-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(517,1,'2018-08-31 10:58:51','2018-08-31 10:58:51','','IMG_1736-opt','','inherit','open','closed','','img_1736-opt','','','2018-08-31 10:59:33','2018-08-31 10:59:33','',287,'http://blog.calloftheforest.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_1736-opt.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(518,1,'2018-08-31 11:00:25','2018-08-31 11:00:25','<h3>Welcome</h3>\r\n<p>Yay, we\'re so excited you\'ve made it to our website!  I have a feeling that you are an individual who understands that what you choose to eat has a direct effect on your health, your overall wellbeing, the earth and all her beings.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>For the love of food</h3>\r\n<p>Choosing plantbased food doesn\'t mean forgoing the enjoyment of food or the pleasure we get from eating.  After all <a href=\"/aya/products\">Aya Original</a> was created because the meltiness of butter is not something anyone should have to miss out on!</p>\r\n<p>More than taste Aya is clean, honest and simple. Clean because we use organic, non-GMO ingredients which means our ingredients are grown with natural, organic fertilisers and pesticides and do not undergo any toxic processing. Honest because we will always be transparent about our ingredients, how our products are made and their health risks. Simple because the healthiest food is found in nature and less processing is best.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What is Aya</h3>\r\n<p>Aya Original is a new generation organic plantbutter for spreading, coo