ters their unique melt-in-the-mouth quality just like dairy butter.</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"term\">NO GMO</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"term\">NO DAIRY</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"term\">NO GLUTEN</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"term\">NO PLASTIC</span> - We package our plantbutters in <b>compostable packaging</b> and we will never use plastic.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Who is Aya</h2>\r\n<b>Aya is a west African Goddess of forests, she protects the forest and its animals and she teaches her tribe how to use the plants to sustain and heal themselves. We chose the name Aya because we align with her values.</b>\r\n<img src=\"http://blog.calloftheforest.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/aya-forest.jpg\" alt=\"aya-forest\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-562\" />\r\n','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','287-revision-v1','','','2018-09-04 15:15:06','2018-09-04 15:15:06','',287,'http://blog.calloftheforest.com/287-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(573,1,'2018-09-04 15:16:43','2018-09-04 15:16:43','<h2>Aya Original</h2>\r\n<img src=\"http://blog.calloftheforest.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/aya-product-2.png\" alt=\"aya-product-2\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-567\" />\r\n<p>Aya Original is our first offering.  We chose Aya Original as our first product because it is the closest organic plantbased alternative to dairy butter.  It\'s <span class=\"emphasis\">creamy</span>, <span class=\"emphasis\">melty</span> and has a <span class=\"emphasis\">delicious, delicate</span> flavour.  We would like everyone to choose Aya Original over dairy butter because plantbutter has a four times lower carbon footprint than dairy butter and has no association with animal cruelty often linked to the conventional dairy industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We encourage you to try Aya on warm toast (so melty and scrummy) and bread (creamy and soft), for cooking (think mushrooms sizzling in plantbutter) or for baking (substitute Aya for butter).</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Dietary and lifestyle</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"ayaList\">\r\n 	<li>ONLY ORGANIC INGREDIENTS</li>\r\n 	<li>No PALM OIL</li>\r\n 	<li>No GMO INGREDIENTS</li>\r\n 	<li>No DAIRY OR LACTOSE</li>\r\n 	<li>Suitable for VEGANS and VEGETARIANS</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Ingredients</h3>\r\n<p>The plant oils in Aya Original are coconut oil, cacao butter and safflower oil. The coconut oil and cacao butter have been steamed to remove their flavours. Cacao butter is what makes Aya so melty, it also helps it stay hard at room temperature. The safflower oil is cold pressed which is a great way of maintaining its nutritional benefits.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Organic steamed coconut oil, organic steamed cocoa butter, organic cold-pressed safflower oil , spring water, Himalayan pink salt , organic sunflower lecithin</strong> (vegetable fat spread 71%)</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Typical nutritional values per 100g</h3>\r\n<table class=\"table table-striped\"><colgroup> <col /> <col /></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr valign=\"TOP\">\r\n<td width=\"50%\">Typical values</td>\r\n<td width=\"50%\">Per 100g</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign=\"TOP\">\r\n<td width=\"50%\">Energy (kJ/kCal)</td>\r\n<td width=\"50%\">2636 / 636</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign=\"TOP\">\r\n<td width=\"50%\">Total fat</td>\r\n<td width=\"50%\">71g</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign=\"TOP\">\r\n<td width=\"50%\">Saturated</td>\r\n<td width=\"50%\">42g</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign=\"TOP\">\r\n<td width=\"50%\">Carbohydrates</td>\r\n<td width=\"50%\">0g</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign=\"TOP\">\r\n<td width=\"50%\">Sugar</td>\r\n<td width=\"50%\">0g</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign=\"TOP\">\r\n<td width=\"50%\">Fibre</td>\r\n<td width=\"50%\">0g</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign=\"TOP\">\r\n<td width=\"50%\">Protein</td>\r\n<td width=\"50%\">0g</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign=\"TOP\">\r\n<td width=\"50%\">Salt</td>\r\n<td width=\"50%\">1.34g</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>How is Aya Original made?</h3>\r\n<p>The oils are melted to liquid form. Whilst cooling the oils are blended with sprin