ines. Our organic cold-pressed safflower oil is from <a href=\"http://www.meridianfoods.co.uk/\">Meridian</a> and originates from India.</p>\r\n<h3>What are the health risks associated with Aya Original?</h3>\r\n<p>Aya Original contains 10% less overall fat and 9% less saturated fat then cow\'s butter. Aya Original has a total fat content of 71%, of which 42% is saturated fat. Coconut oil and cocoa butter are the main contributors to the saturated fat content. Safflower oil is a healthy fat composed of predominantly poly-unsaturated fat. Aya Original should be consumed responsibly as eating high levels of saturated fat can raise your cholesterol and increase your risk of heart disease.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aya Original contains 0.7% sunflower lecithin which makes it creamy and spreadable. Sunflower lecithin contains &lt;1g of trans-fat per 100g.</p>','Products','','inherit','closed','closed','','343-revision-v1','','','2018-09-04 15:22:15','2018-09-04 15:22:15','',343,'http://blog.calloftheforest.com/343-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(579,1,'2018-09-04 16:21:52','2018-09-04 16:21:52','<h2>Aya Original</h2>\r\n<img src=\"http://blog.calloftheforest.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/aya-product-2.png\" alt=\"aya-product-2\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-567\" />\r\n<p>Aya Original is our first offering.  We chose Aya Original as our first product because it is the closest <b>organic plantbased alternative to dairy butter</b>.  It\'s <span class=\"emphasis\">creamy</span>, <span class=\"emphasis\">melty</span> and has a <span class=\"emphasis\">delicious, delicate</span> flavour.  We would like everyone to choose Aya Original over dairy butter because plantbutter <a href=\"http://www.conservationmagazine.org/2014/03/butter-vs-margarine-environmental/\"><b>has a four times lower carbon footprint than dairy butter</b></a> and has no association with animal cruelty often linked to the conventional dairy industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"blue\">We encourage you to try Aya on